  id: wfo_cec_tf_03
  displayName: Student Missile Startup
  description: At the technology forum, a small start-up presents their newly developed
    next-generation ballistic missile system. The team, made up of ambitious university
    students, claims their design could drastically improve missile efficiency and
    battlefield impact. They approach you directly and ask for investment to complete
    the project. If their claims are true, this system could revolutionize war technology
    and make future conflicts far easier to manage.
